description: Every Sunday, 3-7:30 pm at The Wicket Hall (Strathcona Hotel). For those in need of the 'Sunday Blues Services'. Come on down and get your 'soul' blessed with the best live blues In Victoria BC. It's an open mic jam, whether you play or sing. Jammers, bring your instrument and show up early to sign up for your spot to play. Everyone welcome, dancing is encouraged.
